summary.span: 定義可以指派給主體的已知宣告類型之常數。

span.span: Defines constants for the well-known claim types that can be assigned to a subject.

summary.span: 這個類別無法被繼承。

remarks.format: ## Remarks 這些常數定義 Uri 的已知宣告類型。These constants define URIs for well-known claim types.
